[p 
	"This game is a little similar to 
	[em 
		[a href=/Game/61 
			"Bubble Bobble
		]a
	]em
	". Players defeat hordes of enemies in each of fifty stages, only progressing when all enemies are gone. Enemies can either be turned into snowballs or killed by rolling a snowball over them. Unlike 
	[em 
		"Bubble Bobble
	]em
	", though, there is a boss fight every ten stages.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"This is a one-player run through the game, which obsoletes the old 
	(__wikiLink|980M|two-player TAS)
	". Though using two players is faster in some levels, a multiplayer run is slower overall due to the time taken for both players to play the unskippable bonus games.
]p
